    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and will require significant work to become roadworthy again. The exterior shows heavy wear, including several noticeable dents, peeling clear coat, and rust spots on the wheel arches. Mechanically, the engine runs roughly and requires immediate attention, and the transmission has begun to slip during gear changes. The interior has sustained considerable wear with tears in the upholstery and non-functional electronics. This is an ideal project car or parts donor for someone with the right tools and expertise.",
