    {
      "id": "sybil_10_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_10",
      "description": "Offered is a concours-level E46 M3, representing the pinnacle of atmospheric engineering. The S54 inline-six features a flawlessly synchronized double-VANOS system and individual throttle bodies, delivering linear power to an 8,000 RPM redline. This example utilizes the desirable Getrag six-speed manual transmission and a variable M-differential lock for optimal torque distribution. The chassis is structurally immaculate, with proactive subframe reinforcement and a suspension geometry that remains tight and responsive. Every component, from the factory-spec bushings to the pristine Nappa leather interior, remains in showroom condition, free of mechanical fatigue or cosmetic patina. A true turn-key investment for the purist.",
